			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">From: Katina's Beastlord Guide, General Info Submenu, Racial Traits Info...
<br />

<br />
There are 5 races that can currently become beastlords, <span style="font-weight: bold">I always tell people to choose whatever race you like</span>, but so you dont feel 'cheated' by not knowing... There is a list of pro's and con's of every race Below... I've also made a Racial Point Guide, designed to give new beastlords an idea on where to put points. Now choose the race below for the starting stats and recommended point distributions:
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Purpose of this Guide:</span> To explain the Pro's and Con's of each Race...
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Racial Traits, Pro's &amp; Con's</span>
<br />

<br />
This Guide is going to list only the Pro's, Con's, and Traits of each race.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Barbarians</span>
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">General Evaluation:</span>
<br />

<br />
- Decently built for Melee and Casting, Good Str/Sta, Decent Wis.
<br />

<br />
- Good Aligned--Barbarians can travel in most cities unharmed
<br />

<br />
- Cannot travel to Neriak, Oggok, Grobb, or Cabilis(evil racial cities) safely
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Pro's:</span>
<br />

<br />
- Save vs. Cold bonus
<br />

<br />
- Can SLAM(1 point hit--but can inturrupt casting)
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Con's:</span>
<br />

<br />
- Small racial EXP penalty(5%)
<br />

<br />
- No Nightvision
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Iksar</span>
<br />

<br />
<u>General Evaluation:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Better Casting-oriented race, High Wis(for beastlords), but low str/sta
<br />

<br />
- KoS in all racial cities but Shar Vahl
<br />

<br />
<u>Pro's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Infravision
<br />

<br />
- Save vs. Fire Bonus
<br />

<br />
- Regen 2x Normal regen rate.
<br />

<br />
- Natural Swimming(100)
<br />

<br />
- Forage(50)
<br />

<br />
- Natural AC Bonus
<br />

<br />
<u>Con's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Save vs. Cold Penalty
<br />

<br />
- ~20% racial EXP penalty
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Ogres</span>
<br />

<br />
<u>General Evaluation:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Evil, Allied with Dark Elves and Trolls
<br />

<br />
- Awsome Strength &amp; Stamina, definatly a tank-build race, be sure to up your wisdom and dex though
<br />

<br />
<u>Pro's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Can SLAM(1 point hit--but can inturrupt casting)
<br />

<br />
- Infravision
<br />

<br />
- Cannot be stunned by melee attacks from the front
<br />

<br />
<u>Con's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- ~15% racial EXP penalty
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Trolls</span>
<br />

<br />
<u>General Evaluation:</u>
<br />

<br />
- High Stamina, Good Str, Low wis, great melee race.
<br />

<br />
- Evil, Allied with Dark Elves and Ogre's
<br />

<br />
<u>Pro's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Can SLAM(1 point hit--but can inturrupt casting)
<br />

<br />
- Infravision
<br />

<br />
- Regen 2x Normal regen rate.
<br />

<br />
<u>Con's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- ~20% racial EXP penalty
<br />

<br />
- Large Save vs. Fire Penalty
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Vah Shir</span>
<br />

<br />
<u>General Evaluation:</u>
<br />

<br />
- The 'average' race, str/sta/wis all average
<br />

<br />
- KoS to Iksars, trolls, ogres, and most likely dark elves too--but generally welcome in Norrath
<br />

<br />
<u>Pro's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Infravision
<br />

<br />
- Innate Safe Fall (50)
<br />

<br />
- Innate Sneak (50)
<br />

<br />
- No Racial EXP Penalty
<br />

<br />
<u>Con's:</u>
<br />

<br />
- Consumes food 2x faster
<br />

<br />
- There's a 90% Vah-Shir Beastlord population!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
